headline: Palantir Defense Cloud Win And Airbus Renewal Versus High-Valuation Debate
summary: Palantir Technologies (NasdaqGS:PLTR) received expanded authorization from the U.S. Defense Information Systems Agency to deploy its cloud and AI platforms on-premises and at the tactical edge for government clients. The company renewed its multi-year contract with Airbus, continuing to power the Skywise aviation data platform and support migration to sovereign cloud environments. These developments arrive as Palantir remains a focal point of Wall Street debate, including a bearish stance...
